<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-footer
        color="green"
        dark
    >
      <v-row
          justify="center"
          class=" text-center"
      >
        <v-col cols="12"
        >Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
          adipisicing elit.</v-col
        >
        <v-col cols="12">
          <v-btn
              v-for="icon in icons"
              :key="icon"
              text
              dark
          >
            <v-icon>{{ icon }}</v-icon>
          </v-btn>
        </v-col>
        <v-col
            cols="12"
            class="align-center"
        >© 2022 Coding Beauty</v-col
        >
      </v-row>
    </v-footer>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "userFooter",
  data: () => {
    return {
      icons: [
        'mdi-facebook',
        'mdi-twitter',
        'mdi-instagram',
        'mdi-youtube',
      ],
    };
  }
}
</script>
